Sri Lanka's Malinga Gets Hat-Trick Against Kenya in Cricket World Cup

-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 
2011-03-01T13:13:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-01/sri-lanka-s-malinga-gets-hat-trick-against-kenya-in-cricket-world-cup.html
Sri Lanka bowler Lasith Malinga took
the second Cricket World Cup hat-trick of his career as Kenya
was all out for 142 in a Group A match in  Colombo  today.  Malinga finished on 6-38.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  